Hall 1
The walls of this hallway are decorated with commemorative plaques with the names of the employ of the year engraved on them. There is a door on the right with the words <Administration Office> on it. The corridor also continues <forward>.

Hall 2
The hallway continues on until another corridor branches off from it to the <left>.  The corridor also continues <forward> with pictures on the wall, of the different logos <courier> had used in the past.

Hall 5
The corridor ends with 3 doors, the one directly ahead has nothing on it however above it on the brick work, in spray painted stencil font, is the word <Warehouse>. The Door to the left has a metal plate screwed to it with the words <Locker Room> etched into it. The door on the right has on it a plate that matches the opposing Locker Room door with the one change that it displays the word <Canteen> on it.
